<br>l) for any proposed or actual merger, acquisition, corporate reorganization, financing, sale joint venture, assignment, transfer, disposition or similar transaction, including the sale of business, assets or stock; and
<br>m) otherwise for everyday business purposes, to comply with law, or in other ways for which we provide specific notice at the time of collection.

